{"tid":719081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報：中國不希望與美國打貿易戰","createTime":"2018-06-27T07:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T04:57:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":82,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"d498713d413a13c72afa7dd89e7efcfe27f2b6a2","tid":719081,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"美國特朗普政府今個星期公布限制中國投資美國的措施，針對「中國製造2025」規劃。內地《環球時報》發表評論文章，指在貿易戰的陰霾正影響投資者情緒及企業股價，中國政府是時候採取自衛措施，向可能受美方不公平政策影響的企業及行業，提供補貼。<br />\n<br />\n文章重申，中國不希望與美國打貿易戰，但如果特朗普持續將中國捲入貿易戰的旋渦，北京第一件要做的事，就是保障中國公司及投資者，按照世貿框架，向中國企業提供出口補貼及政策上的支持，如果中興通訊及其他企業，成為貿易戰的首批受害者，他們會最先得到支持，強調中國政府絕不允許美國傷害中國的科技公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1016058&amp;csid=261_368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1016058%26csid%3D261_368&d=q%2F0ocy0U8FGeelLTiruMvP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=76f7729f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1016058&amp;csid=261_368</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3l4pbm5/19s7000064754p52p33o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3l4pbm5%2F19s7000064754p52p33o.jpg&h=b3e501e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f5908ca15421b0af47feac7afadcf39664882b","tid":719081,"uid":187232,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:31:02.000Z","msg":"少咗句"},{"pid":"98547c672c1c7b2d08b036bca3a9919fd9876f36","tid":719081,"uid":5490,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:32:20.000Z","msg":"亮劍未？<br />\n<br />\n2025"},{"pid":"ffe8e818e048dfbad05168f0c6e7c8204cc97b40","tid":719081,"uid":17008,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:33:16.000Z","msg":"依d新聞除左有錢佬或中國人，基本上全世界都睇完都不禁大喝一聲：「好！」"},{"pid":"50798aaa3a5319300f08e46ae9db25e8cfe61900","tid"